Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.72,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(960,20)\fax-0.12}though it was always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:24.42,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(960,20)\fax-0.12}If I have a tough, iron armor protecting the world
